casebody.head_matter:
SPEEDWAY LLC, et al., petitioners,
v.
Zachary WILSON, et al.
No. 17-1030.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 19, 2018.
Motion of Center for Constitutional Jurisprudence for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Motion of National Conference on Weights and Measures for leave to file a Brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit denied.
Justice ALITO and Justice GORSUCH took no part in the consideration or decision of these motions and this petition.
